sequenceDiagram
    participant Comp as Component
    participant SA as ServerAction
    participant Worker
    participant SW as SendWrapper
    participant D1

    Comp->>SA: dispatch(CreateTodo { title })
    SA->>Comp: Optimistic UI update

    SA->>Worker: HTTP POST /api/create-todo
    Worker->>SW: Route to server fn
    SW->>SW: Wrap in SendWrapper (non-Send env)
    SW->>D1: INSERT INTO todos ...
    D1-->>SW: Ok(row_id)
    SW-->>Worker: Ok(Todo)
    Worker-->>SA: 200 JSON response

    SA->>SA: version.update(|v| v + 1)
    SA->>Comp: Resource refetches (invalidated by version)
    Comp->>Comp: Re-render with confirmed data
